      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUARDIAN (1) jumps from box 1 for the first time after placing latest at this track (17.19) in a T3 RSTW. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Racing well and deserves a win. EXTREME DASH (8) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when third beaten 1.3 lengths (17.25). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Expected to be in the finish again. PARIS MASH (3) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Maiden winner three back (22.81) at Ballarat over 390m. Can feature with the right run. ASTON MACQUARIE (2) drops in journey and should be in the mix.",
